{"tid":1827897,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"班農盛讚協議「小代價打垮中共」","createTime":"2020-01-17T10:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T04:43:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a5fd760ce692c8c668911cc84361a189e9df496f","tid":1827897,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:20:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200117/FOWNWCP5ZVDPHKIGQ7XRXF6XTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200117%2FFOWNWCP5ZVDPHKIGQ7XRXF6XTE%2F&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcylR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=75618aa7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200117%2FFOWNWCP5ZVDPHKIGQ7XRXF6XTE%2F&h=19a19ef6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200117/FOWNWCP5ZVDPHKIGQ7XRXF6XTE/</a><br />\n<br />\n班農盛讚協議「小代價打垮中共」<br />\n<br />\n中方此前向外放風力爭美方撤銷所有加徵關稅，作為達成中美首階段貿易協議的條件，最後如意算盤未能打響，中國官媒卻死不認輸，強調協議帶來雙贏。美國前「國師」班農大讚特朗普堅持關稅，打垮中共。有美國金融巨頭亦認為，中國對美方作出許多讓步。而專家指出，對中國而言，簽署協議比不簽好。<br />\n<br />\n劉鶴與特朗普簽署協議後，中美輿論戰立即開打。特朗普前首席策略師班農認為，美方以極小代價，就把中共打垮，他讚揚特朗普堅持關稅，擊垮中共。美國對沖基金巨頭、海曼資本管理公司創辦人巴斯亦認為，中國實際上作出了許多讓步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200117/large/1579190930_2e27.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200117%2Flarge%2F1579190930_2e27.gif&h=8ef10f08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國大舉增購美國產品，或對國內的製造業造成壓力。 路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家：華可順勢改革經濟<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：劉鶴儍笑淪佈景板 牆內禁言 官媒唱好<br />\n<br />\n中國官媒則積極營造良好氣氛，報道、專家解析與評論皆取態正面，但模糊帶過中方讓步內容。央視「國際銳評」表示，中方堅持的三個核心關切（包括取消全部加徵關稅）及兩項原則（WTO規則與市場原則）在協議中都得到體現。惟央視沒提協議保留了美國對2,500億美元中國貨品的25%關稅。《人民日報》則發表題為《平等．互利．雙贏－專家解讀中美第一階段經貿協議》的長文，稱協議體現「合作共贏」原則。<br />\n<br />\n彼得森國際經濟研究所高級研究員鮑恩指出，若從中方角度看，簽署協議比貿易戰升級好：「中國願意在協議中履行的承諾實際可說對中國有利。政治上可能很難做，但從經濟上講，中國內部一直想推動一些經濟改革。他們很久以前就打算這麽做了。」<br />\n<br />\nCNBC/VOA"},{"pid":"6cf7a8725b2a0bafe01c092b9a546cabed071e14","tid":1827897,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:47:13.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb50bb850618eed277e4a8bfddd82bbb70457b4","tid":1827897,"uid":290443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea28471583a951e1a4d78e2908510c8a24c6315","tid":1827897,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"相關新聞：劉鶴儍笑淪佈景板 牆內禁言 官媒唱好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想睇呢段多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e3d7e4d2cff5a0c78cb55bebeca288fbf913a7","tid":1827897,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ea28471583a951e1a4d78e2908510c8a24c6315","tid":1827897,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"相關新聞：劉鶴儍笑淪佈景板 牆內禁言 官媒唱好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想睇呢段多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5269d1b7630563ffe43b367e9305c8a2d9e4e9","tid":1827897,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"班農：無論你在哪裏，我們已在戰爭中。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v